Name: Playforever mimmo aeroplane yellow
Description:
This vintage winged toy from Playforever is made with contemporary detailing and modern production methods. Thick moldings give the plane weight and quality parts give it gloss. The scale is beautiful to behold. 

Since 2005, Playforever of London has been designing a range of timeless and elegant toys. Over the years, the line which includes many other products has developed its own design language. 

ABS plastic and rubber.  Approx. 11 inches length.  No removable parts.  Age 3+. US CPSIA tested.

Name: Tiger Tribe Sunshine Sounds Rainbow Xylophone
Description:
Another wonderful item from Tiger Tribe. Five  beautiful xylophone drums and two drumsticks that nestle inside each other. 
Eco friendly Bamboo. Sourced from plantation forests, non toxic paints. 
Largest drum 12cm in diameter & 10cm height . Smallest drum 5cm in diameter & 3cm in height 
Recommended age 3 + 
Presented in a cardboard cylinder. 
Cylinder height 16cm , cylinder diameter 18cm
